"1  (3.5-oz.) package fresh shiitake mushrooms*","1/3 cup extra virgin olive oil","2 tablespoons fresh lemon juice","1/2  shallot, minced","1/2 teaspoon table salt","1/2 teaspoon freshly ground pepper","1 1/2 pounds small zucchini","3 tablespoons thinly sliced chives","3 tablespoons chopped fresh basil","1/3 cup chopped toasted, salted pecans","  Freshly grated pecorino or Parmesan cheese"